          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Experimental determination of the proton escape width",
                " in the giant dipole resonance of 89Y."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "E.Van Camp",
                "R.Van De Vyver",
                "E.Kerkhove",
                "D.Ryckbosch",
                "H.Ferdinande",
                "P.Van Otten",
                "P.Berkvens"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REFERENCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "J,PR/C,24,(6),2499,1981",
                "code_unit": [
                  {
                    "unit": "J,PR/C,24,(6),2499,1981",
                    "doi": "10.1103/PhysRevC.24.2499",
                    "field": {
                      "reference_type": "J",
                      "reference": {
                        "code": "PR/C",
                        "number": null,
                        "volume": "24",
                        "part": null,
                        "issue": "6",
                        "page": "2499"
                      },
                      "date": 1981
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "2BLGGHT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "LINAC"
                ],
                "institute": "2BLGGHT"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Ghent State University linac."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "QMPH"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A  nearly  monoenergetic  photon  spectrum was",
                " constructed artificially by taking an algebraic  sum",
                " of suitably normalized bremsstrahlung spectra,  with",
                " consecutive end point energies.",
                " The bremsstrahlung photon beam  was  hardened  by  a",
                " 19.5   cm  thick  graphite  cylinder,  placed  about",
                " half-way between  the  Au  bremsstrahlung  converter",
                " target  with  thickness 90 mg/cm**2 and the reaction",
                " chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A natural 89Y foil with a thickness of 13.3 mg/cm**2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB",
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SILI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Uncooled  solid state detectors with an active",
                " area of 200 mm**2 and a thickness of 3 mm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REL-REF": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "M",
                "subentry_number": null,
                "author": "R.Carchon+",
                "reference": {
                  "code": "J,PR/C,14,456,1976",
                  "field": {
                    "reference_type": "J",
                    "reference": {
                      "code": "PR/C",
                      "number": null,
                      "volume": "14",
                      "part": null,
                      "issue": null,
                      "page": "456"
                    },
                    "date": 1976
                  }
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " The experimental setup description."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Photoproton energy spectra were measured  at  several",
                " bremsstrahlung  end point energies between 14 and 25",
                " MeV,  going up in 1 MeV steps and recalculated  into",
                " reaction   cross   sections   using   the  following",
                " equation:",
                "                E = A/(A-1)Tp + Sp,",
                " where Tp is the photon kinetics energy and Sp denotes",
                " the ground state separation energy (7.07 MeV)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
            {
